  <title>MapCreator3D</title>
  <subtitle>A component for 3D visualization of a catchment area.</subtitle>
  <informaltable>
    <tgroup cols="2">
      <colspec colname="c1" colnum="1" colwidth="1*"/>
      <colspec colname="c2" colnum="2" colwidth="3*"/>
      <thead>
        <row>
          <entry nameend="c2" namest="c1">Metadata</entry>
        </row>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <row>
          <entry>classification</entry>
          <entry>visualization</entry>
        </row>
      </tbody>
    </tgroup>
  </informaltable>
  <sect2>
    <title>Variables</title>
  <informaltable>
    <tgroup cols="2">
      <colspec colname="c1" colnum="1" colwidth="1*"/>
      <colspec colname="c2" colnum="2" colwidth="3*"/>
      <thead>
        <row>
          <entry>Name</entry>
          <entry>Description</entry>
        </row>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <row>
          <entry>stylesFileName</entry>
          <entry>name of SLD-File containing layer style information</entry>
        </row>
        <row>
          <entry>styleID</entry>
          <entry>ID of a style in the SLD-File to be used for mapping</entry>
        </row>
        <row>
          <entry>hrus</entry>
          <entry>name of the HRU attribute to be used for mapping</entry>
        </row>
        <row>
          <entry>showAttr</entry>
          <entry>list of attributes used for mapping</entry>
        </row>
        <row>
          <entry>numOfRanges</entry>
          <entry>number of ranges to classify attributes</entry>
        </row>
        <row>
          <entry>rangeColor</entry>
          <entry>color to shade ranges</entry>
        </row>
        <row>
          <entry>shapeFileName1</entry>
          <entry>name of shapefile to map additional layers</entry>
        </row>
        <row>
          <entry>shapeFileName2</entry>
          <entry>name of shapefile to map additional layers</entry>
        </row>
        <row>
          <entry>shapeFileName3</entry>
          <entry>name of shapefile to map additional layers</entry>
        </row>
        <row>
          <entry>shapeColors</entry>
          <entry>colors for additional shapefiles</entry>
        </row>
        <row>
          <entry>baseShape</entry>
          <entry>original name of shapefile</entry>
        </row>
        <row>
          <entry>heightMap</entry>
          <entry>filename of a height map of the catchment area </entry>
        </row>
        <row>
          <entry>resolution</entry>
          <entry>horizontal/vertical resolution of the calculated 3D model</entry>
        </row>
        <row>
          <entry>light</entry>
          <entry>switch for light of 3D model</entry>
        </row>
      </tbody>
    </tgroup>
  </informaltable>
  </sect2>
    <sect2>
    <title>Component Description</title>
      <para>It creates an interactive three-dimensional visualization of the catchment area.
      Spatially distinct attributes of the hrus attribute can be projected on the map's surface. The
      layer style can be adjusted by using an sld file and color shades. Extra shape layers can be
      added.</para>
  </sect2>
</sect1>
